== Overview ==
The "Puncher" class Shield Neutraliser uses a netronic wave to cause massive amounts of damage to enemy shields.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Shield Neutraliser can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in Vulcore.
